---
// Hero Section — Neukonzept: ganzheitliches Coaching für Männer 40+
// Siehe "konzept 2026.md" Abschnitt 4 (ABC-Hybrid)
---

<section class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Animated gradient rings (dezent gehalten – Orange-Fokus liegt auf dem CTA) -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center pointer-events-none">
    <div class="absolute w-[300px] h-[300px] rounded-full border border-orange/10 animate-ping" style="animation-duration: 4s;"></div>
    <div class="absolute w-[500px] h-[500px] rounded-full border border-orange/5 animate-ping" style="animation-duration: 6s; animation-delay: 1s;"></div>
    <div class="absolute w-[700px] h-[700px] rounded-full border border-orange/5 animate-ping" style="animation-duration: 8s; animation-delay: 2s;"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Navigation -->
  <nav class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 z-20 p-6 flex justify-between items-center">
    <a href="/" class="text-xl font-bold text-text-primary">
      Daniele Pauli <span class="gradient-text">Coaching</span>
    </a>
    <a href="/survey/" class="btn-secondary text-sm py-2 px-4 flex items-center gap-2">
      <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4" />
      </svg>
      Ich 2.0 Check
    </a>
  </nav>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <div class="section-container text-center relative z-10 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Badge -->
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 glass px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-8 animate-fade-up">
        <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-orange rounded-full animate-pulse"></span>
        <span class="text-sm text-text-secondary">Ganzheitliches Coaching für Männer 40+</span>
      </div>

      <!-- Headline -->
      <h1 class="heading-xl mb-6 animate-fade-up delay-100">
        <span class="text-text-primary">Wieder</span>
        <span class="gradient-text text-glow">voll da.</span>
      </h1>

      <!-- Subtitle -->
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-text-secondary mb-5 max-w-3xl mx-auto animate-fade-up delay-200">
        Mehr Energie, weniger Bauch, klarer Kopf — ohne Crash-Diät,
        ohne stundenlanges Cardio, ohne dich zu verbiegen.
      </p>

      <!-- Empathie-Zeile -->
      <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-text-secondary/70 italic mb-10 animate-fade-up delay-300">
        Müdigkeit ist kein Charakterfehler. Sie ist ein Signal.
      </p>

      <!-- CTA Buttons -->
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center animate-fade-up delay-400">
        <a
          href="/survey/"
          class="btn-primary glow-orange-hover group"
        >
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4" />
          </svg>
          Mach den Ich-2.0-Check
          <span class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">→</span>
        </a>
        <button
          onclick="Calendly.initPopupWidget({url: 'https://calendly.com/danielepauli'});return false;"
          class="btn-secondary"
        >
          Kostenloses Erstgespräch
        </button>
      </div>

      <!-- Mikro-Trust-Zeile -->
      <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary/60 mt-6 animate-fade-up delay-400">
        2-Minuten-Check · unverbindlich · kostenlos
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Scroll indicator -->
  <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 animate-bounce">
    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-orange" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
    </svg>
  </div>

  <!-- Quote -->
  <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-8 max-w-xs hidden md:block">
    <p class="text-text-secondary/60 italic text-sm">
      "Stark sein heisst: ein Leben lang voll da sein."
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
